author: David Fischer
title: visvim Presents Its New Spring/Summer 2017 Collection
text:
Visit the original post to see all 30 images from this gallery. 
Japanese brand visvim is back with yet another compelling collection for Spring/Summer 2017. By now the brand’s signature is very clear – vintage Americana inspired, with a Japanese influence and of course an un-compromising drive to the absolute best quality that can stand the test of time.
The new visvim Spring/Summer 2017 collection features strong outerwear, fantastic denim, and some eye-catching knitwear pieces, next to a stellar line-up of accessories. Check out the full new lookbook in the above gallery.
